<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Company Registration Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: blanchedalmond;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .success-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #A82400;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .success-icon i {
            color: white;
            font-size: 40px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #A82400;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .details-section {
            background-color: #fff8ee;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #f2e6d9;
        }
        .company-details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f2e6d9;
        }
        .detail-label {
            flex: 1;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #A82400;
        }
        .detail-value {
            flex: 2;
            color: #555;
        }
        .status-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            background-color: #A82400;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .timeline {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .timeline-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .timeline-dot {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #d9d0c3;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .timeline-dot.active {
            background-color: #A82400;
        }
        .timeline-dot.pending {
            background-color: #d48f7d;
        }
        .timeline-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }
        .timeline-content h4 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            color: #A82400;
        }
        .timeline-content p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #777;
        }
        .next-steps {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff8ee;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #f2e6d9;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #A82400;
        }
        .steps-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #A82400;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            background-color: #7e1c00;
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-header">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
            </div>
            <h1>Application Submitted Successfully!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Your company registration application has been received.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="details-section">
            <div class="company-details">
                <h3>Company Information</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Company Name:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><%=companyData.name%></div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Registration ID:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><%=companyData.registrationNumber%></div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Business Type:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><%=companyData.industry%></div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Submitted On:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><%=companyData.time%></div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Contact Email:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value"><%=companyData.contactEmail%></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-section">
            <h3>Current Status</h3>
            <div class="status-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Pending Verification
            </div>
            <p>
                Our team is currently reviewing your application and the submitted documents.
                This process typically takes 2-3 business days.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline">
            <h3>Registration Progress</h3>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot active"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>Application Submitted</h4>
                    <p><%=companyData.time%></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot pending"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>Document Verification</h4>
                    <p>In Progress</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>Registration Approved</h4>
                    <p>Pending</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h4>Certificate Issuance</h4>
                    <p>Pending</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>Next Steps</h3>
            <ul class="steps-list">
                <li>We will verify all the documents you've submitted</li>
                <li>You will receive email updates about your application status</li>
                <li>If additional information is needed, our team will contact you</li>
                <li>Once approved, you'll receive your official registration certificate</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can check your application status anytime by logging into your account.</p>
            <a href="/community/<%=community._id%>/company" class="action-button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing our service for your company registration needs.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Business Registration Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>